message.body: Hi there, it's Jenny! So I have to go to Swarthmore this afternoon and will be there through dinner. I will probably leave there around 8ish. If that's not too late I can come by on my way home. If tomorrow is better just let me know!
Great! I will text you when I'm nearby
Hey, thanks for coming by. You (and Trevor) should come by more often!
Thanks for having me! It was great to catch up! We would love to hang out!
